page.title: 09Sutton on Sea High St.
page.content: Most of the shops are on the High St.On the left,facing the sea,there is an estate agent, Barclays Bank,a garage,Lloyds and Midland Banks, the Post Office,the newsagents,a sweet shop,and greengrocer's. There is another estate agent,a hardware shop,the Park Tavern,a bakery,the Dolphin fish and chip shop, a shoe shop,a pet shop,a clothes shop,the Anchor Restaurant and a fruit shop.On the other side,heading back, there is a bookshop, Cafe, Chemist, Butcher, Clothes Shop,the Bacchus Hotel, Antiques Shop, Hair Dressers, Spar Grocers.Next is Evergreen Walk with a florist,an Antique Shop and a Gift Shop. Back on the High St. are a cafe with laundrette,a grocery shop, estate agent and a sewing a knitting shop and a fish and chip shop.There are other shops not on the High St.
